---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Plenum AI Systems"
  description="Plenum AI Systems, a Lead Continuity LLC company, builds self-hosted AI revenue infrastructure for home service businesses. Founded by Vinicius Libero Moreira."
  ogTitle="About — Plenum AI Systems"
  ogDescription="Private AI infrastructure built by an engineer, not an agency."
  canonical="https://plenumaisystems.com/about"
>
  <Nav />

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="label">About</div>
      <h1>An engineer, not an agency.</h1>
      <p>I build production AI infrastructure for businesses that are tired of losing revenue to slow follow-ups and silent phones.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-photo">
          <img src="/assets/headshot.webp" alt="Vinicius Libero Moreira — Founder, Plenum AI Systems" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="margin-top:0;">
            I'm <strong style="color:var(--text);">Vinicius Libero Moreira</strong> (Vini) — full-stack developer, Technical Project Manager, and founder of <strong style="color:var(--text);">Plenum AI Systems</strong>, a brand operated by <strong style="color:var(--text);">Lead Continuity LLC</strong>. With 5+ years building production systems in Ruby on Rails, Python, and AI automation, I don't outsource. I architect, build, and deploy every stack myself.
          </p>
          <p>
            Plenum AI Systems is a self-funded operation. No VC money. No bloated team. One engineer solving one problem: home service businesses lose revenue because their follow-up is too slow and their dead lead databases are collecting dust.
          </p>
          <p>
            I serve clients globally — from HVAC contractors in the US to agencies in Europe and Latin America — with enterprise-grade infrastructure at affordable prices. My background in regulated sectors means your data sovereignty isn't a buzzword. It's how I build.
          </p>
          <p>
            The goal is simple: <strong style="color:var(--orange);">make home service businesses impossible to ignore</strong> — by answering every call, reactivating every dead lead, and generating every review they've been leaving on the table.
          </p>
          <div class="about-metrics">
            <div>
              <div class="about-metric-val">5+</div>
              <div class="about-metric-lbl">Years building</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="about-metric-val">10+</div>
              <div class="about-metric-lbl">Production workflows</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="about-metric-val">1</div>
              <div class="about-metric-lbl">Engineer</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="about-metric-val">∞</div>
              <div class="about-metric-lbl">Commitment</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Exists -->
  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="label">Why Plenum Exists</div>
      <h2>The problem that started it all.</h2>
      <p>The average business takes <strong style="color:var(--text);">42 hours</strong> to respond to a lead. By then, the lead has already bought from someone else. Meanwhile, their CRM database is full of contacts they paid to acquire — and never contacted again.</p>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon orange" style="font-size:1.5rem;">?</div>
          <h3>The Gap</h3>
          <p>AI tools exist. Cheap cloud hosting exists. But no one is bundling them into a turnkey revenue infrastructure that a local HVAC company can deploy in a weekend. Agencies sell strategy. I sell running systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon blue" style="font-size:1.5rem;">!</div>
          <h3>The Stakes</h3>
          <p>Every missed call is a job they'll never know about. Every dead lead is money left on the table. Every silent customer is a review that was never asked for. The leak is real — and it's massive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon green" style="font-size:1.2rem;">✓</div>
          <h3>The Philosophy</h3>
          <p>Self-hosted infrastructure. No SaaS lock-in. You own your pipeline, your data, and your customer relationships. I build the engine — you drive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon silver" style="font-size:1.2rem;">⚡</div>
          <h3>The Difference</h3>
          <p>This isn't a chatbot widget. It's a fully managed AI stack that answers phones, follows up with leads, reactivates databases, and grades your sales team — 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="label">How We Work</div>
      <h2>No fluff. No jargon. Deployed in weeks.</h2>
      <p>Every engagement follows the same three-step process — proven across dozens of clients in different sectors.</p>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-node">01</div>
          <h3>Audit the Leaks</h3>
          <p>I map where you're losing revenue: missed calls, slow follow-ups, dead databases, silent customers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-node">02</div>
          <h3>Deploy the Stack</h3>
          <p>You focus on closing deals. I handle everything else. I build, deploy, and proactively monitor your entire AI pipeline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-node">03</div>
          <h3>Watch Revenue Recover</h3>
          <p>Instant responses. Reactivated leads. Auto-generated reviews. You track ROI from day one in your own dashboard.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Business Info (A2P compliance) -->
  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="label">Business Information</div>
      <h2>Lead Continuity LLC DBA Plenum AI Systems</h2>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:32px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Legal Entity</h3>
          <p><strong style="color:var(--text);">Lead Continuity LLC</strong><br>
            Doing Business As (DBA): <strong style="color:var(--text);">Plenum AI Systems</strong><br>
            EIN: <span style="color:var(--text3);">[EIN PENDING]</span><br>
            Industry: Marketing / Media
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Contact Details</h3>
          <p>
            30 N Gould St Ste N<br>
            Sheridan, WY 82801<br>
            United States<br><br>
            � +1 (307) 296-4737<br>
            ✉️ <a href="mailto:contact@plenumaisystems.com">contact@plenumaisystems.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Want to know who you're working with?</h2>
      <p>I'm transparent about what I build and how I build it. If we're a fit, great. If not, I'll point you in the right direction.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">→ Get in Touch</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn btn-blue">View Services</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
